title.name: CA CERT OF TITLE OR SALVAGE ACQ
title.copartNotes: CA - Only members holding an active Dealer, Dismantler or Exporter License will receive CA transferrable documents to obtain a Clear Title on this lot. After the sale, all other members not holding one of the above licenses will receive an AC (California Acquisition Bill of Sale). After successful completion of required CA inspections the AC may be revived to a CA Certificate of Title with Salvage Branding. www.dmv.ca.gov

title.name: CA SALVAGE ACQUISITION BILLOFSALE
title.copartNotes: CA - All members will receive an AC (California Acquisition Bill of Sale). After successful completion of required CA inspections the AC may be revived to a CA Certificate of Title with Salvage branding. www.dmv.ca.gov
